metadata.month_transition: Transitions from October to November at entry 7 (11/3/93)

insights: October-November 1993 flights - spans two months within single page
Clear notation of 'Puerto Rican trip' for Jeffrey & Ghislaine on 10/9/93
TGB emerges as primary hub with most departures and arrivals
CVG likely refers to Cincinnati airport - major US mainland connection
CUN likely Cancun - suggests Caribbean/Mexico travel pattern
Adrian becomes frequent travel companion with Jeffrey in October
November shows return of group travel patterns with larger passenger lists
SA EV appears to be abbreviated passenger name - possibly 'Sarah' and 'Eve'
All flights maintain consistent 1.5 hour duration - shorter than previous months
Aircraft category coding appears in right columns (1 4 1 1 and 1 8 1 1 patterns)
Dorothy reappears in November after absence in October entries
Steve Villiers returns at end of November maintaining previous pattern
Large group flights bookend the page (Oct 7 and Nov 12) with 8 passengers each
Eric appears multiple times in November suggesting regular travel companion
